**Summary:**
This documentation covers the Android-Kotlin SDK for Amplitude analytics, including installation via Gradle/Maven with `com.amplitude:analytics-android` dependency, configuration options like `flushIntervalMillis`, `flushQueueSize`, and `autocapture` settings, event tracking with `track()` and `identify()` methods, autocapture features for sessions/app lifecycles/screen views/deep links/element interactions, user groups, revenue tracking, plugins system, and advanced features like COPPA control, advertising ID/app set ID usage, location tracking, and offline mode with network connectivity checking.

